I let myself in.

284
00:14:13,923 --> 00:14:16,002
Chestnut can talk?

285
00:14:16,003 --> 00:14:18,103
Thank you, God!

286
00:14:20,503 --> 00:14:22,962
What's up, good looking?

287
00:14:22,963 --> 00:14:24,342
I still can't believe

288
00:14:24,343 --> 00:14:26,172
