298
00:14:50,593 --> 00:14:52,882
I mean, I'm not Mother Teresa.

299
00:14:52,883 --> 00:14:55,002
You bought the diner?

300
00:14:55,003 --> 00:14:57,252
The diner that doesn't
show up on Google Maps

301
